  content: "In line with the most powerful elements of Agile philosophy, the new site was released almost immediately, alongside the old site. No clunky, delayed, high stress site changeover. New functionality was being released early and often, directly in line with user feedback. Our team co-located with Plymouth University, living in a specially rented flat in Plymouth."

