  content: "We worked with the team responsible for maintaining the website’s 10,000+ pages of content and adding new material. Kanban tools were taught to improve efficiency and give performance metrics, with the result that duration of the commissioning and uploading process dropped dramatically. The Ruby on Rails skills of the internal team so they can maintain the site efficiently going forward."

team_quote:
  quote: "Unboxed Consulting excelled in that they were able to put a team down in Plymouth to skill up our in-house team, something that many suppliers are unwilling to do."
